The Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources is hereby authorized to issue the corresponding Special Patent in the name of the Republic of the Philippines-Court of Appeals.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 29th day of June , in the year of Our Lord, Twenty Hundred and Ten.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) LEANDRO R. MENDOZA Executive Secretary

